def myfun1(x,tissue):
    if x["0"]==tissue:
        return x["log2FoldChange"]
    elif x["1"]==tissue:
        return -1*x["log2FoldChange"]

q_concat = pd.DataFrame()
for tissue in tissues:
    t1 = df_as[df_as['contrast'].str.contains(tissue)]
    t1 = t1.sort_values(['sig','gene']).drop_duplicates(['gene'],keep='last')
    t2 = tss[tss["3"].isin(t1[t1['sig']=="noSig"]["gene"])]
    t3 = tss[tss["3"].isin(t1[t1['sig']=="sig"]["gene"])]
    bf1 = bf.overlap(t2,rbp,cols1=["0","1","2"],cols2=["0","1","2"])
    bf2 = bf.overlap(t3,rbp,cols1=["0","1","2"],cols2=["0","1","2"])
    c1 = bf1["5_"].value_counts()/t2.shape[0]
    c2 = bf2["5_"].value_counts()/t3.shape[0]
    a = c2/c1
    a = a.sort_values(ascending=False).dropna().head(20)
    q1 = pd.DataFrame(a)
    q1['tissue'] = tissue
    q_concat = pd.concat([q1,q_concat])

import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

# 创建绘图
plt.figure(figsize=(6,5))
ax = sns.barplot(data=go, y="Description", x="-log10(Padj)", color='skyblue', orient='h')

# 获取 x 的最大值，用于确定文本放置位置（放在柱子内部）
x_max = go['-log10(Padj)'].max()
# 设置一个内边距比例，例如从 10% 开始放置文本
padding_ratio_start = 0.1

# 遍历每个条形，添加文本
for i, (idx, row) in enumerate(go.iterrows()):
    x_val = row['-log10(Padj)']
    # 将文本放在柱子内部，靠近开始处
    text_x_start = x_val * padding_ratio_start  # 起始位置
    ax.text(text_x_start, i, row['Description'], 
            color='black',  # 根据背景颜色选择合适的字体颜色
            fontsize=10, 
            va='center',    # 垂直居中对齐
            ha='left')      # 水平左对齐

# 隐藏原始的 y 轴标签（因为我们已经在柱子内显示了）
ax.set_yticks([])  # 移除 y 轴刻度和标签
ax.set_ylabel('')  # 隐藏 y 轴标题

# 可选：调整 x 轴标签位置，避免重叠
plt.xlabel('-log10(Padj)')
plt.title('GO')
plt.tight_layout()
# plt.savefig("/home/zhaoying/workbai/NC/Figure2/AS_GO.pdf")
plt.savefig("/home/zhaoying/workbai/NC/Figure2/Figure2K.pdf")
plt.show()
